  "summary": {
    "en": "An entry-level 72-piece fort kit for compact secret bases, tent frames, and family gift programs.",
    "zh": "入门级72件堡垒拼搭套装，适合小型秘密基地、帐篷框架和家庭礼品项目。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 72-piece set is designed for compact forts, small tents, and beginner-friendly indoor building projects.",
      "Lightweight PP rods and connector balls are easy for children to handle and suitable for repeated assembly.",
      "The simple pole-and-ball system supports spatial awareness, hands-on coordination, and cooperative play.",
      "A practical color box and storage bag make the item suitable for retail, promotional gifts, and OEM/ODM customization."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "72件套适合搭建小型堡垒、小帐篷和入门级室内拼搭项目。",
      "轻便PP杆件与连接球便于儿童操作，也适合反复拆装。",
      "简单的杆球拼接系统有助于空间认知、动手协调和协作玩耍。",
      "实用彩盒和收纳袋配置适合零售、促销礼品和OEM/ODM定制。"
    ]
  },
